sequenceDiagram
    participant App
    participant Config as StorageConfig
    participant Json as kotlinx.serialization

    App->>Config: Create WebDavConfig(name, url, user, pass)
    Config-->>App: Immutable config instance

    App->>Config: withEnabled(false)
    Config-->>App: New disabled copy

    App->>Json: encodeToString(config)
    Json-->>App: JSON string

    App->>Json: decodeFromString(json)
    Json-->>App: Restored config
